# Capacity Valuation
###############################################################################

This file introduces the abstract notion of a derived valuation
specific to agent capacity.

Capacity valuation evaluates effective, usable capacity
under structural, contextual, and agreement-mediated conditions.

It does NOT:
• judge competence or merit
• imply entitlement or authority
• assert legitimacy or morality
###############################################################################
